snippet.title: 【DOAXVV】New Venus Release! Introducing Patty
snippet.description:
A new Venus "Patty" (CV: Marika Kohno) has arrived in "DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!"
Enjoy the beginning of a new Vacation with the "pure", "young", "unguarded" woman, raised on Venus Islands.
○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com/
○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/
Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：10 April 2019 (Wednesday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in steam
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
